title: Video: "The Great British Baking Show" Collection 12 - Official Trailer - Netflix | TheFutonCritic.com
text: The Great British Baking Show: Collection 12 | Official Trailer | Netflix The Great British Baking Show follows a group of amateur bakers as they compete against each other in a series of challenges, attempting to impress judges Paul Hollywood and Prue Leith with their baking skills. One contestant is eliminated each week, and the winner is selected from the contestants who reach the finals. Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81608923 OFFICIAL TRAILER DEBUT + US DATE ANNOUNCEMENT The Great British Baking Show Collection 12 Bakers, start your ovens! A new group of contestants gathers in the tent to mix, roll and decorate their way to the top prize. Series Premiere Date: September 27, 2024 *new episodes air every Friday Format: Unscripted Series (10 x 60-minute episodes) Read More About This Season's Bakers on Tudum Synopsis: The Great British Baking Show follows a group of amateur bakers as they compete against each other in a series of challenges, attempting to impress judges Paul Hollywood and Prue Leith with their baking skills. One contestant is eliminated each week, and the winner is selected from the contestants who reach the finals. Executive Producers: Letty Kavanagh, Richard McKerrow, Kieran Smith, Jenna Mansfield Production Company: Love Productions www.netflix.com/TheGreatBritishBakingShow
